  "title": "Third-Party Risk Manager (1-Year Contract)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Drive the continuous improvement of the firm-wide Outsourcing and Third-Party Risk Management (TPRM) framework, utilizing an integrated approach to assess and mitigate risks for new and existing suppliers.</p></li><li><p>Enhance and oversee the governance model to ensure robust monitoring of risks posed by both intra-group and external third parties.</p></li><li><p>Optimize the Supplier Risk Management platform while maintaining the highest standards of data integrity.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Continuously update the third-party risk assessment framework to ensure strict adherence to evolving regulatory guidelines and industry initiatives.</p></li><li><p>Identify and escalate critical concerns regarding third-party relationships, with a specific focus on concentration risk and fourth-party risk exposures.</p></li></ul><p><br />To apply online please use the 'apply' function.</p><p><strong>(EA: 94C3609/ R24124496)</strong></p>",
